    "127131422": {
      "title": "Encyclopedia of the Peoples of Asia and Oceania",
      "abstract": "Aboriginal Australians Acehnese Armenians Armenians: nationality Bactrians Bengalis Dravidians Durranis East Timorese: nationality Fijians, Indigenous Filipino Muslims Han Harappans Hawaiians Hmong Indo-Aryans Indo-Fijians Indonesians: nationality Japanese Kiribatese: nationality Kyrgyz Maldivians: nationality Manchus Micronesians Other Backward Classes (OBC) Persians, Sassanids Polynesians Punjabis Rapanui Rroma Russians, Asian Samoans: nationality Scheduled Castes Scheduled Tribes Scythians Taiwanese: nationality Tajiks Tats and Mountain Jews."
